reviewText: At first when purchasing this DVD from my local music store I had mixed views about how good this release by Nickelback would be. All I can say is that I was not at all disappointed but infact please beyond my wildest imagination.The canadian band played in their home city and to a raucaus reception played their hearts out. Good song, good picture, great quality sound. The band were professional in their undertaking and were a pleasure to listen and watch. This DVD is a must for any fan new or old of Nickelback, who have gone from classic rock into the alternative mainstream rock arena.
summary: A absolute must for any Nickelback fan!
